title: Open Season - Full Screen Special Edition(MKV)
description:
PG | 1h 23min | Animation, Adventure, Comedy | September 29th 2006




Boog, a domesticated 900lb. Grizzly bear, finds himself stranded in the woods 3 days before Open Season. Forced to rely on Elliot, a fast-talking mule deer, the two form an unlikely friendship and must quickly rally other forest animals if they are to form a rag-tag army against the hunters.




Directors: Roger Allers, Jill Culton

Writers: Steve Bencich (screenplay), Ron J. Friedman (screenplay)

Stars: Ashton Kutcher, Martin Lawrence, Debra Messing




English,French and Spanish audio and subtitles on the feature, English audio only on the extras
